f name=\"bilb\"/>\n|21\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n== Certifications ==\n{{certification Table Top}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Australia|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|certyear=1991|relyear=1991|certref=<ref name=ryan>{{cite book|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|title=Australia's Music Charts 1988\u20132010|year=2011|publisher=Moonlight Publishing|location=Mt. Martha, VIC, Australia}}</ref>}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Canada|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|number=4|certyear=1996|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=France|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Gold|certyear=2001|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Japan|artist=\u30de\u30e9\u30a4\u30a2\u30fb\u30ad\u30e3\u30ea\u30fc|title=\u30a8\u30e2\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u30ba|award=Platinum|number=4|certyear=1996|relyear=1991|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.riaj.or.jp/issue/record/1996/199611.pdf |title=RIAJ > The Record > November 1996 > Highest Certified International Albums/Singles (Mar '89 - Sep '96) |work=[[Recording Industry Association of Japan]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=January 30, 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110091234/http://www.riaj.or.jp/issue/record/1996/199611.pdf |archivedate=January 10, 2015 }}</ref>|salesamount=1,000,000|salesref=<ref name=\"sales\"/>}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Netherlands|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|certyear=1994|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=New Zealand|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|certyear=1992|relyear=1991|recent=website|id=3497|certref=<ref>{{cite book|author=Dean Scapolo|title=The Complete New Zealand Music Charts 1966-2006|publisher=RIANZ|year=2007|isbn=978-1-877443-00-8}}</ref>}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Sweden|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|certyear=1992|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=Switzerland|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Gold|certyear=1994|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=United Kingdom|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|certyear=1992|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017}}\n{{certification Table Entry|type=album|region=United States|artist=Mariah Carey|title=Emotions|award=Platinum|number=4|certyear=1994|relyear=1991|accessdate=August 31, 2017|salesamount=3,595,000|salesref=<ref name=\"ussales\"/>}}\n{{Certification Table Summary}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Worldwide|salesamount=8,000,000|salesref=<ref name=\"sales\"/>|nocert=yes}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n'''Works cited '''\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{Cite book\n | ref = harv\n | last = Nickson\n | first = Chris\n | title = Mariah Carey revisited: her story\n | year = 1998\n | publisher = [[St. Martin's Press]]\n | isbn = 978-0-312-19512-0\n }}\n* {{Cite book\n | ref = harv\n | last = Shapiro\n | first = Marc\n | title = Mariah Carey: The Unauthorized Biography\n | publisher = [[ECW Press]]\n | year = 2001\n | isbn = 978-1-55022-444-3\n }}\n{{refend}}\n\n{{Mariah Carey}}\n\n[[Category:Mariah Carey albums]]\n[[Category:1991 albums]]\n[[Category:Columbia Records albums]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Walter Afanasieff]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by David Cole (record producer)]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Carole King]]\n[[Category:Albums involved in plagiarism controversies]]\n", "name_user": "Ironman1p", "label": "safe", "comment": "Album sales", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emotions_(Mariah_Carey_album)"}
